quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Deε wͻn a wͻ’nni anidaasoͻ sε wͻ’ne Yεn behyia no keka ne sε: “Adεn nti na yensiane Soro abͻfoͻ ma yεn, anaa yennhunu ye’Wura Nyankopͻn no? Ampa sε wͻn ara ama wͻn ho so, na wͻ’ate atua ama no aboro so kεse"
  25,22,"Ɛda a wͻ’behunu Soro abͻfoͻ no, saa da no εnnyε asεmpa mma abͻneεfoͻ no. (Soro abͻfoͻ no) bεka sε: “Moma εhyeε kεseԑ nna (wͻn ne Soro Aheman mu foͻ no ntεm)“"
  25,23,"Yε’bεba dwuma biara a (abͻneεfoͻ no) diiε no so, na Yε’bεma no ayε sε mfuturo bi a atu ahweteε"
  25,24,"Ɛda no, Soro aheman no mu foͻ no benya asetena pa ne ahomegye bea pa"
  25,25,"Ɛda no a mununkum bεma ɔsoro mu adwidwa, na Soro abͻfoͻ besiane siane paa no"
  25,26,"Saa Da no Ahennie paa no wͻ Ahummͻborͻ Hene no. Saa Da no, εbεyε den ama (Kaafirfoͻ) boniayεfoͻ no"
  25,27,"Saa Da no na (onipa) bͻnefoͻ no bεka nensa aka sε: “Mehunui a anka mekaa Ɔsomafoͻ no ho ne no faa kwan (pa) no so"
  25,28,"Ao, Adi ayε me, Mehunui a anka manfa asomasi yͻnkoͻ”"
  25,29,“Ampa paa sε wama m’ayera afri Afutusεm no ho wͻ berε a yεde berεε me no. Ͻbonsam (yε obi a) odi onipa hwammͻ paa”
  25,30,"Ɔsomafoͻ no nso bεka sε: ”Me Wura Nyankopͻn, nokorε sε, menkorͻfoͻ no yii wͻn ani frii Qur’aan yi so”"
  25,31,Saa ara na Yε’maa Nkͻmhyεni biara tamfo wͻ abͻneεfoͻ no mu. Nanso wo Wura Nyankopͻn som bo (ma wo) sε Ɔkwankyerεfoͻ ne Ͻboafoͻ
  25,32,"Deε wͻn a wͻ’nnye nnie no ka ne sε: “Adεn nti na yensiane Qur’aan no mmͻ mu mma no prεko?” (Ye’siane no saa) sεdeε εbεma w’akoma agyina pintinn, na Yε’kenkan (Qur’aan no ma wo) nkakra nkakra, hyehyɛ no pɛpɛɛpɛ"
  25,33,"(Nkͻmhyεni), mfatoho biara a wͻ’de bεba (abεko atia) woͻ (anaa wͻ’de besum wo fidie) no, Yε’de nokorε no a (wode beyi wͻn ano) ne nkyerεkyerεmu pa paa bεberε wo"
  25,34,"Wͻn a yεbεboa wͻn ano (wͻ Atemmuda ama wͻn anante) wͻ wͻn anim akͻ Amane-hunu gya no mu no, wͻn na wͻn wͻ gyina berε bͻne mu paa, na wͻn na wͻn ayera afri kwan (tenenee) no soͻ"
  25,35,"Ampa sε Yε’de Nwoma no maa Mose, na Yε’de ne nua Aaron kaa ne ho sε ͻboafoͻ anaasε ͻkyeame"
  25,36,"Yε’kaa sε: ”Monkͻ amanfoͻ no a wͻ’fa Yεn Nsεm no atorᴐsԑm no hͻ. Enti Yε’sεee wͻn pasaa"
  25,37,"Noa nkorͻfoͻ no nso, εberε a wͻ’buu asomafoͻ no atorᴐfoᴐ no, Yε’maa nsuo faa wͻn. Yε’de wͻn yεε nsεnkyerεnee anaasε adesua maa adasamma. Abͻneεfoͻ no deε Y’asiesie asotwee a εyε ya paa ato wͻn hͻ"
  25,38,"Ɛna Aad ne Samuud ne Rassifoͻ, ne awoͻ ntotoasoͻ bebree a wͻ’bedii ntamu hͻ no"
  25,39,"Yε’yεε mfatoho maa wͻn mu biara, na wͻn mu biara nso Yε’sεee wͻn pasaa"
  25,40,"Ampa sε (Quraishfoͻ) kͻtwam wͻ kuro no a Yε’tͻͻ nsutͻ bͻne guu wͻn soͻ no mu. Enti εyaa na wͻ’nnhu anaa? Daabi, wͻn ani nna Owusͻreε (da) no so"
  25,41,"Sε (boniayεfoͻ) no hu wo a wͻ’di wo ho fεw sε: ”Enti woi na Nyankopͻn ayi no sε Ɔsomafoͻ"
  25,42,"Ɛkaa kakraabi sε, sε yannya aboterε a anka ͻyeraa yεn frii yεn anyame no ho”. Ɛberε a wͻ’behunu asotwee no na wͻ’behunu obi a wayera afri ͻkwan pa no soͻ"
  25,43,"(Nkͻmhyεni), w’ahunu obia wafa n’apεdeε ayε nyame no? Enti wobεyε okyitaafoͻ ama (saa nipa) no"
  25,44,"Anaa wodwen sε wͻn mu dodoͻ no tie, anaasε wͻ’te (deε woka kyerε wͻn no) ase? Wͻ’tesε nyεmmoa, daabi, wͻn ayera afri kwan (tenenee) no so"
  25,45,Wonhunuu sεdeε wo Wura Nyankopͻn si fa twe sunsum mu. Sε Ɔpε a anka Ɔbεma no agyina faako. Nanso Yε’de awia ayε kwankyerε (anaa nyinasoͻ) ama no
  25,46,Afei na Y’atwe no nkakra-nkakra de aba Yεn hͻ
  25,47,"Ɔno na W’ayε anadwo akatasoͻ ama mo, εna (W’ayε) nna nso ahomegyeε, εna W’ayε adekyeε nso a (mode) sͻreε (tesε deε obi asͻre afri owuo mu)"
  25,48,"Ɔno na Ɔsoma mframa sε anigyesεm dedi N’ahummͻborͻ no (a εne nsutͻ) no anim kan, εna Osiane nsuo a εho teε fri soro"
  25,49,"De nyane asaase a awuo, εna Yε’dema nyεmmoa a Ya’bͻ, ne nnipa pii ma wͻ’nom"
  25,50,"Ampa sԑ Y’akᴐso akyerԑkyerԑ (Nsԑm no) mu yie akyerԑ wᴐn sԑdeԑ wᴐbԑkaekaeԑ anaa wᴐ’de betu wᴐn ho foᴐ, nanso nnipa pii mpԑ (Nokorԑ no) na mmom wᴐ’kᴐ so yi boniayԑ"
  25,51,"Sε Yε’pε a, anka Yε’bεsoma kͻkͻbͻni wͻ kuro biara so"
  25,52,"Enti (Nkͻmhyεni), entie (Kaafirfoͻ) boniayεfoͻ no, na fa (Qur’aan no) kotia wͻn nko dene mu paa"